content.html:
Hi, I’m Osama

I’m a freelance graphic designer with over six years of experience, having worked with restaurants, social media influencers, small businesses, and a variety of creative clients. Yet, it’s books that truly capture my heart. My passion for stories led me to specialize in book cover design—where I get to blend my love for art with the magic of storytelling.

Born and raised in Jordan and now based in Spain, I’ve been lucky enough to work with authors from different cultures, infusing my designs with a mix of vibrant tradition and modern flair. I believe every book deserves a cover that’s as unique and captivating as the story within it.

My Design Philosophy

Designing a book cover isn’t just about making something look good—it’s about creating a visual handshake between you and your reader. When we work together, it’s more than just a project; it’s a creative journey where your vision takes center stage.

I start by getting to know you and your book—your inspirations, your target audience, and even those little details that make your story one-of-a-kind. From there, I dive into brainstorming and sketching ideas, carefully crafting concepts that capture the essence of your narrative. We’ll refine every detail until the cover feels like it was made just for you..

Ready to give your book the cover it truly deserves? Let’s chat and create something extraordinary together.
content.markdown:
**Hi, I’m Osama**

I’m a freelance graphic designer with over six years of experience, having worked with restaurants, social media influencers, small businesses, and a variety of creative clients. Yet, it’s books that truly capture my heart. My passion for stories led me to specialize in book cover design—where I get to blend my love for art with the magic of storytelling.

Born and raised in Jordan and now based in Spain, I’ve been lucky enough to work with authors from different cultures, infusing my designs with a mix of vibrant tradition and modern flair. I believe every book deserves a cover that’s as unique and captivating as the story within it.

## **My Design Philosophy**



Designing a book cover isn’t just about making something look good—it’s about creating a visual handshake between you and your reader. When we work together, it’s more than just a project; it’s a creative journey where your vision takes center stage.

I start by getting to know you and your book—your inspirations, your target audience, and even those little details that make your story one-of-a-kind. From there, I dive into brainstorming and sketching ideas, carefully crafting concepts that capture the essence of your narrative. We’ll refine every detail until the cover feels like it was made just for you..

Ready to give your book the cover it truly deserves? Let’s chat and create something extraordinary together.

en.heading: How do I get started with my project?

en.subheading: Partner with a design expert dedicated to your success.

items.title: What is the typical turnaround time for a cover design?

description.html: Standard projects typically take 1–2 weeks, depending on complexity and revisions. If you have a tight deadline, let us know—we offer expedited services for urgent projects.
description.markdown: Standard projects typically take 1–2 weeks, depending on complexity and revisions. If you have a tight deadline, let us know—we offer expedited services for urgent projects.

items.title: What if I’m not satisfied with the final design?

description.html: Don’t worry, we offer unlimited revisions to ensure you get the cover of your dreams. If, however, you're still not satisfied, we will cancel the project free of charge.
description.markdown: Don’t worry, we offer unlimited revisions to ensure you get the cover of your dreams. If, however, you're still not satisfied, we will cancel the project free of charge.

description.html: A 50% deposit is required to start the project, with the remaining balance due upon final approval. We accept various payment methods, including credit cards and PayPal, to keep things simple and secure.
description.markdown: A 50% deposit is required to start the project, with the remaining balance due upon final approval. We accept various payment methods, including credit cards and PayPal, to keep things simple and secure.

items.title: Do you design covers for all genres?

description.html: Absolutely. Our team has extensive experience working across a wide range of genres—from literary fiction and fantasy to thriller, romance, non-fiction, and more—ensuring that your cover appeals to your specific target audience.
description.markdown: Absolutely. Our team has extensive experience working across a wide range of genres—from literary fiction and fantasy to thriller, romance, non-fiction, and more—ensuring that your cover appeals to your specific target audience.

items.title: Can I provide my own images or design ideas?

description.html: Yes! We welcome your input. Whether you have inspirational images, sketches, or specific elements you’d like incorporated, we’ll work with your ideas to create a polished, professional cover that aligns with your vision and meets technical publishing standards.
description.markdown: Yes! We welcome your input. Whether you have inspirational images, sketches, or specific elements you’d like incorporated, we’ll work with your ideas to create a polished, professional cover that aligns with your vision and meets technical publishing standards.

items.title: I already have a published book. Can you redesign my cover?

description.html: Certainly. We offer redesign services to refresh or update existing covers. Whether you need minor tweaks or a complete overhaul, our team will collaborate with you to update your cover while preserving the essence of your original design.
description.markdown: Certainly. We offer redesign services to refresh or update existing covers. Whether you need minor tweaks or a complete overhaul, our team will collaborate with you to update your cover while preserving the essence of your original design.

items.title: Do you offer additional services beyond cover design?

description.html: Yes. In addition to custom cover design, we provide complementary services such as 3D mockups, and promotional banner design. If you have any special requirements, just let us know at the start, and we can tailor our services to meet your needs.
description.markdown: Yes. In addition to custom cover design, we provide complementary services such as 3D mockups, and promotional banner design. If you have any special requirements, just let us know at the start, and we can tailor our services to meet your needs.
